# Contributing Guidelines

Thank you for your interest in contributing to Vexel Innovations.

## Important
This is a proprietary repository. Contributions are only accepted from authorized collaborators.

## Guidelines
- Follow project coding standards
- Keep commits clean and descriptive
- Do not introduce breaking changes without approval
- All contributions must be reviewed

## Process
1. Create a feature branch
2. Make your changes
3. Submit a pull request
4. Await review and approval

Unauthorized contributions will be rejected.
